== Requirements

Ruby! You can get 1.8.7 from http://www.ruby-lang.org/

=== Updating rubygems

  gem update --system

=== Gems

* libxml-ruby
* rmagick
* activesupport

  gem install libxml-ruby rmagick activesupport

=== If you're on windows

* Download ImageMagick and rmagick gems from http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=12&release_id=27880

Install .exe first, then .gem (with gem install).
